{EDUCATION} {ST PETERS}HAS 11 TEACHERS AND 348 PUPILS.IT HAS 12 CLASSROOMS.5 TEACHERS ARE INFANT 7 ARE JUNIOR.THE SCHOOL HAS BEEN THERE 181 YEARS.THE HEAD HAS BEEN THERE 8 YEARS .THERE ARE PLANS TO REBUILD THE SCHOOL ON THE PRESENT PLAYING FIELDS.THE SCHOOL COLOURS ARE RED,WHITE AND GREY.
{SLADE ROAD} HAS 8 TEACHERS AND 213 PUPILS.THERE ARE 3 INFANT TEACHERS AND 4 JUNIOR.THE SCHOOL HAS BEEN THERE SINCE 1914.THE SCHOOL COLOUR IS BLUE.THE SCHOOL CLUBS INCLUDE YOGA, FOOTBALL, CHESS AND ART.THERE IS ALSO HOCKEY,CRICKET AND ATHLETICS.
